info.author: Nordic Semiconductor ASA
info.description: A Python interface and library for pc-ble-driver. This allows Python applications to interface with a Nordic Semiconductor IC (both nRF51 and nRF52 series) over a serial port to obtain access to the full serialized SoftDevice API.
info.keywords: nordic nrf51 nrf52 ble bluetooth softdevice serialization bindings pc-ble-driver pc-ble-driver-py pc_ble_driver pc_ble_driver_py
info.name: pc-ble-driver-py
info.summary: Python bindings for the Nordic pc-ble-driver SoftDevice serialization library
